46:19.736 --> 46:21.522
The food's supposed to be great.

46:21.655 --> 46:23.896
Come on. A guy told me about a place.

46:25.575 --> 46:29.443
The cops thought they were being fired on.
They were being fired on.

46:29.579 --> 46:32.321
