And they weren't being fired on.

46:32.457 --> 46:36.041
— The only people firing guns were cops.
— Toni, how can you know that?

46:37.128 --> 46:38.243
Terry.

46:40.674 --> 46:42.539
All right, fuck it. You know what?

46:43.468 --> 46:45.424
I guess it'll all get sorted out.

46:45.553 --> 46:49.546
(Chuckles) Yeah.
Well, thanks for giving me copies of these.

46:49.683 --> 46:53.221
When are you gonna stop harassing
the musicians on Jackson Square?

46:53.353 --> 46:55.594
Oh, are we gonna fight about that too?

46:59.359 --> 47:00.599
How's Sofia?

47:02.779 --> 47:05.395
Depressed, angry, anxious.

47:05.532 --> 47:06.692
Aren't we all?

47:06.825 --> 47:08.907
Everybody is out of their minds.

47:10.996 --> 47:13.908
— How are yours?
— Fine. I guess.

47:14.749 --> 47:18.287
