on the phone, it's always monosyllables

47:18.420 --> 47:21.207
and, you know, multitasking.
I can always tell.

47:21.339 --> 47:22.499
"Yeah.

47:22.632 --> 47:23.963
"Uh—huh.

47:24.092 --> 47:25.878
"Sure, Dad.

47:26.011 --> 47:27.000
