47:27.137 --> 47:29.002
Sounds familiar.

47:31.891 --> 47:33.631
It's been six months.

47:34.644 --> 47:35.929
Seven.

47:37.313 --> 47:39.224
Things getting any better?

47:40.150 --> 47:41.765
Worse, I'd say.

47:45.071 --> 47:46.607
Talk about it?

47:47.782 --> 47:50.649
It was an accident.
That's what she knows.

47:57.500 --> 47:58.706
Mmm.

48:00.754 --> 48:01.960
Everything OK here?

48:02.088 --> 48:04.921
Fantastic.
What do you call this thing again?

48:05.050 --> 48:09.259
Uh, Frenchuletta. It's our version
of a Muffuletta, served on French.

48:09.387 --> 48:10.718
Really?

48:10.847 --> 48:13.884
Muffuletta. Ooh!

48:14.017 --> 48:15.097
Got it.

48:15.226 --> 48:18.935
Pontchartrain, Tchoupitoulas, muffaletta...
I'm learning stuff.

48:19.064 --> 48:21.146
Listen, I'll take the other half with me.

48:21.274 --> 48:23.060
All right, I'll get you a go box, baby.

48:23.193 --> 48:25.309
— Thank you, darling.
— You're welcome.

48:26.362 --> 48:28.444
Look at this thing.
It's the size of la verga mia.

48:28.573 --> 48:30.359
I gotta take a picture of that.

48:31.367 --> 48:34.359
I love this town.
Why didn't anybody tell me about it before?

48:34.496 --> 48:37.158
I've been calling you for the last six months,
trying to get you down here.

48:37.290 --> 48:40.077
You never said how great it was. You just said
there was dinero lying in the streets.

48:40.210 --> 48:41.871
— Yeah.
- Hey...

48:42.003 --> 48:45.370
you know a place we can
go hear some music tonight?

48:46.299 --> 48:48.164
Cuz, cuz, cuz!

48:49.010 --> 48:50.546
There's more to life than money.

49:02.524 --> 49:04.230
